pfunc_expr_unrecognised_word: pgkla mqnuqu ：ungat klaan mkla ka patas "$1".
pfunc_expr_unexpected_operator:
pnqtaan mqnuqu ：ida mksaw kiya ka $1 patas pnskraya smpug.
(sspug：dmuuy kska kari elug eudabitaqpnskraya patas sspug. Kiya o+ - * / > < = )
pfunc_expr_missing_operand:
pgkla mqnuqu ：msula $1 ka patas smpung yeyn.
(smpung yeyn：kska euda patas sspug nii o wada jiyun sspug ddpatas, ga muda smpung jiyun kska elug kari patas nii：+ - * / tmaga pnskrya)
pfunc_expr_unrecognised_punctuation: pgkla mqnuqu ：ungat klaan pgkla ka pnskraya "$1".
